object.name: ISS astronauts perform final spacewalk of Expedition 66
object.content: Expedition 66 astronauts Raja Chari and Matthias Maurer ventured outside the International Space Station on Wednesday, performing a spacewalk to carry out repairs and upgrades on the space station.
